short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Check your speed with Radix Clicks

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Test your Clicks Per Second in 8 different modes now! Also, get to know how fast you can click with a detailed click-tracking-map.

CPS test stands for Click-Per-Second test. It can be a 1/3/5/10/15/30/60/100-second simple test. 

You need to click as many times as possible before time's up. Feel free to try as many times as you want.
